    <node id="Raf" maxvalue="1">
      <value val="1">
        <exp str="Ras | !(Rheb | AKT | ERK)"/>
      </value>
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P04049"/>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P10398"/>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P15056"/>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.pubmed.com/19437514"/>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.pubmed.com/20963626"/>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.pubmed.com/14963045"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>&lt;Description&gt;
Serine/threonine-protein kinase that acts as a regulatory link between the membrane-associated Ras GTPases and the MAPK/ERK cascade, and this critical regulatory link functions as a switch determining cell fate decisions including proliferation, differentiation, apoptosis, survival and oncogenic transformation. 
&lt;/Description&gt;

&lt;HGNC&gt;
RAF1
ARAF
BRAF
&lt;/HGNC&gt;

&lt;Uniprot&gt;
P04049 (RAF1_HUMAN)
P10398 (ARAF_HUMAN)
P15056 (BRAF_HUMAN)
&lt;/Uniprot&gt;

&lt;Observation&gt;
Expressed in AGS.
No known mutations in AGS.
Reported to be active in unperturbed AGS cells in 2 publications (19437514, 20963626) and inactive in 1 publication (PMID 14963045)
&lt;/Observation&gt;</comment>
      </annotation>
      <nodevisualsetting>
        <ellipse x="856" y="364" width="80" height="30" backgroundColor="#cccccc" foregroundColor="#000000"/>
