      </value>
      <annotation>
        <linklist>
          <link xlink:href="http://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/P18146"/>
        </linklist>
        <comment>&lt;Description&gt;
Transcriptional regulator. Recognizes and binds to the DNA sequence 5'-CGCCCCCGC-3'(EGR-site). Activates the transcription of target genes whose products are required for mitogenesis and differentiation.
&lt;/Description&gt;

&lt;HGNC&gt;
EGR1
&lt;/HGNC&gt;

&lt;Uniprot&gt;
P18146 (EGR1_HUMAN)
&lt;/Uniprot&gt;

&lt;Observation&gt;
Expressed in AGS.
No known mutations in AGS.
Reported to be inactive in unperturbed AGS cells in 1 publication (PMID 15155664)
&lt;/Observation&gt;</comment>
